Package grafioschtrader.gtnet.model.msg

Class LastpriceExchangeMsg

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.gtnet.model.msg.LastpriceExchangeMsg
public class LastpriceExchangeMsg extends Object
Payload for intraday price exchange messages (GT_NET_LASTPRICE_EXCHANGE_SEL_C, GT_NET_LASTPRICE_PUSH_SEL_C). In a request: - Contains instruments with their current local timestamps - Timestamps can be null (meaning no local data, requesting any available price) In a response: - Contains only instruments where the provider has more recent prices than the request - Includes full OHLCV price data
